When you update code you'll need to verify it. To check code you can choose appropriate method(s) in:

- Run `task test-compile` and `task test-unit`
- Run command like ` npx mocha --config test/unit/.mocharc.json ./test/unit/path/to/test.spec.ts`

Do not:

- Create a temporary test file
